OL,3,CPortsmouth v Southampton disorder:
OL,4,CImages of fans released
OL,6,FPolice investigating disorder after a
OL,7,Ffootball match between Portsmouth and
OL,8,FSouthampton have released photos of 13
OL,9,Ffans they would like to speak to.
OL,11,FThe appeal follows incidents that
OL,12,Foccurred after the EFL Championship
OL,13,Ftie between the two rival clubs at
OL,14,FFratton Park on Sunday 25 January.
OL,16,FAfter the full-time whistle, some fans
OL,17,Fwere involved in disorder including
OL,18,Fcriminal damage to the stadium, with
OL,19,Fseats being ripped out of the stands
OL,20,Fand thrown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
