OL,3,CPortsmouth v Southampton disorder:
OL,4,CImages of fans released
OL,6,FCoins, bottles and pieces of broken
OL,7,Fseats were also thrown.
OL,9,FPolice say they have already
OL,10,Finterviewed a number of individuals in
OL,11,Frelation to these incidents and would
OL,12,Fnow like the public's help in
OL,13,Fidentifying the remaining people.
OL,15,FChief Superintendent Simon Dodds, who
OL,16,Fwas Gold commander for the match,
OL,17,Fsaid: "We understand the passion
OL,18,Ffootball fans have for their clubs,
OL,19,Fand the extra excitement that builds
OL,20,Faround these derby matches.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
