OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777313467
OL,3,CPortsmouth v Southampton disorder:
OL,4,CImages of fans released
OL,6,F"The vast majority of fans at both
OL,7,Fmatches this season were able to show
OL,8,Ftheir support in the right way and
OL,9,Fwe're really thankful for that.
OL,11,F"We've really appreciated the support
OL,12,Fand positive comments from both sets
OL,13,Fof fans and local communities who have
OL,14,Fthanked us for helping to ensure both
OL,15,Fgames could go ahead without any major
OL,16,Fdisruption.
OL,18,F"However, we are taking action against
OL,19,Fthose who have used these events as an
OL,20,Fexcuse to behave in a manner that puts
OL,21,Fothers at risk of serious injury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU
