OL,3,CPortsmouth v Southampton disorder:
OL,4,CImages of fans released
OL,6,F"The events were captured on CCTV and
OL,7,Fwe are now asking for your help to
OL,8,Fidentify several people ` from both
OL,9,Ffanbases ` who we would like to speak
OL,10,Fto.
OL,12,F"If you are one of the people in these
OL,13,Fphotos, or know who they are, please
OL,14,Fcall 101 quoting reference
OL,15,F44260128696."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
